Sentencas: In this work, porous YFe0.5Co0.5,O-3 (YFC) thin sheets were-synthesized by citric acid method.
Titulo: Porous YFe0.5Co0.5O3 thin sheets as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The crystal structure, morphology, thermal expansion, electrical conductivity, and electrochemical properties of YFC were investigated to evaluate it as a possible cathode on BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2O3 (BZCY) electrolyte for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (ITSOFCs).
Titulo: Porous YFe0.5Co0.5O3 thin sheets as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: An orthorhombic perovskite structure was observed in YFC.
Titulo: Porous YFe0.5Co0.5O3 thin sheets as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The conductivity of YFC is 183 S cm (-1) at 750 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Porous YFe0.5Co0.5O3 thin sheets as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The coefficient of thermal expansion of composite cathode YFC-BZCY is closer to BZCY electrolyte than YFC.
Titulo: Porous YFe0.5Co0.5O3 thin sheets as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The composite cathode represents a relatively low polarization resistance (R-P) of 0.07 Omega cm(2) at 750 degrees C in air due to the porous thin sheet-like cathode.
Titulo: Porous YFe0.5Co0.5O3 thin sheets as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The oxygen reduction reaction process and the reaction activation energy of cathode were also analyzed.
Titulo: Porous YFe0.5Co0.5O3 thin sheets as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: An anode-supported cell of NiO-BZCY IBZCY IYFC-BZCY is fabricated by a simple method of co-pressing.
Titulo: Porous YFe0.5Co0.5O3 thin sheets as cathode for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
